盧比茨于1987年12月18日出生于[[西德|联邦德国]][[莱茵兰-普法尔茨|莱茵兰-普法尔茨]]州的[[蒙塔鲍尔|蒙塔鲍尔]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Webb |first=Sam |url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/who-andreas-lubitz-everything-you-5404476 |title=Who is Andreas Lubitz? Everything you need to know about the Germanwings co-pilot |work=[[Daily_Mirror|Daily Mirror]] |location=[[London|London]] |accessdate=2015-03-27 |archive-date=2018-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181015165422/https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/who-andreas-lubitz-everything-you-5404476 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，家中生活富裕<ref name="中新网"/>，父亲是商界高管，母亲是钢琴老师。卢比茨是[[犹太|犹太]]姓，关于他的种族未知。他于14岁时开始学习驾驶[[滑翔机|滑翔机]]，并参加飞行俱乐部<ref name="telegraph1">{{cite web |last=Sawer |first=Patrick |url=http://qz.com/370582/what-we-know-so-far-about-andreas-lubitz-the-co-pilot-who-deliberately-crashed-the-germanwings-plane/ |title=What we know so far about Andreas Lubitz, the co-pilot who "deliberately" crashed the Germanwings plane |work=Te |accessdate=2015-03-28 |archive-date=2019-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190413113147/https://qz.com/370582/what-we-know-so-far-about-andreas-lubitz-the-co-pilot-who-deliberately-crashed-the-germanwings-plane/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其个人梦想是要立志成为飞行员，在他房间里有许多汉莎航空的标志，同时持有滑翔机飞行执照<ref name="中新网">{{cite news |title=德翼空难人为因素显现 副机师背后动机引发热议 |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2015/03-29/7166895.shtml |publisher=中国新闻网 |date=2015-03-29 |accessdate=2015-03-29 |archive-date=2015-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150329125550/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2015/03-29/7166895.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=曾因抑郁中断学飞 德国之翼副驾卢比茨其人 |url=http://news.carnoc.com/list/310/310119.html |publisher=民航资源网 |date=2015-03-27 |accessdate=2015-03-29 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402152900/http://news.carnoc.com/list/310/310119.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。高中毕业后，他开始接受[[汉莎航空|汉莎航空]]飞行培训，并于2008年开始在[[德国|德国]][[不来梅|不来梅]]和[[美国|美国]][[亚利桑那州|亚利桑那州]][[固特異_(亞利桑那州)|固特異]]参加训练<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.azcentral.com/story/news/nation/2015/03/26/arizona-pilot-learned-to-fly-goodyear/70481268/ |title=Officials: German pilot in crash trained in Goodyear|date=2015-03-26|work=The Arizona Republic|location=|accessdate=2015-03-28 |quote=Ruecker said Lubitz also trained in Goodyear, Arizona.}}</ref>。在完成11个月的训练后，盧比茨开始担任[[乘务员|乘务员]]<ref name="telegraph1"/>。

他于2013年9月进入[[汉莎航空|汉莎航空]]下属子公司[[德国之翼|德国之翼]]担任飞行员。在飞机失事之前，他总共飞行了630个小时<ref name="telegraph1"/>。盧比茨还曾经是[[汉堡王|汉堡王]]的[[临时工|临时工]]，经理人评价他是一个“可靠并不起眼”的人<ref name="guardianlive">{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/mar/27/germanwings-crash-details-emerge-of-the-co-pilot-who-crashed-his-plane-live-updates|title=Germanwings crash: report that co-pilot Lubitz had suffered 'personal life crisis'|work=The Guardian|date=2015-03-27|accessdate=2015-03-27|archive-date=2019-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430080212/https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/mar/27/germanwings-crash-details-emerge-of-the-co-pilot-who-crashed-his-plane-live-updates|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他还曾经于2011年、2012年和2013年参加[[法兰克福|法兰克福]]半程马拉松<ref name="telegraph1"/>。

卢比茨曾有一个女朋友，她说“卢比茨是一个精神饱受折磨、性格古怪的人，善于隐藏内心阴暗的想法的人”<ref>{{cite news |title=副驾驶前女友透露内情 |url=http://news.hexun.com/2015-03-29/174502767.html |publisher=泉州晚报 |date=2015-03-29 |accessdate=2015-03-29 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402122155/http://news.hexun.com/2015-03-29/174502767.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外，卢比茨还梦想駕駛更大的長途客機，如[[波音747|波音747]]或[[空中客车A380|空中客车A380]]<ref>{{cite news |title=【廉航空難】拍檔爆料 盧比茨夢想駕747或A380 |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20150330/53582332 |publisher=苹果日报 |date=2015-03-30 |accessdate=2015-03-30 |archive-date=2015-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150330225109/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20150330/53582332 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

卢比茨长期患有严重的[[憂鬱症|憂鬱症]]。2009年，卢比茨曾因“严重憂鬱症”中断了飞行训练，并接受了18个月的心理观察，美国方面也曾将他列入不适宜飞行的名单<ref name="qq">{{cite news |title=德国坠机副驾驶曾被美国列入不适宜飞行名单 |url=http://news.qq.com/a/20150328/006180.htm |publisher=中国青年报 |date=2015-03-28 |accessdate=2015-03-29 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402120613/http://news.qq.com/a/20150328/006180.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年2月，卢比茨在[[杜塞尔多夫大学|杜塞尔多夫大学]]医院接受医疗诊断，但并未透露具体病情，院方表示该症状不是忧郁症<ref name="qq2">{{cite news |title=德航“最后8分钟”：副驾驶多次怂恿机长上厕所 |url=http://news.qq.com/a/20150330/001103.htm?tu_biz=1.114.2.1 |publisher=中国新闻网 |date=2015-03-30 |accessdate=2015-03-30 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402124842/http://news.qq.com/a/20150330/001103.htm?tu_biz=1.114.2.1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根据杜塞尔多夫大学医院发出的声明，卢比茨曾于2015年3月10日接受抑郁症治疗<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uniklinik-duesseldorf.de/presse/detailansicht/article/co-pilot-der-germanwings-maschine-war-zu-untersuchungen-im-universitaetsklinikum-duesseldorf|title=Co-Pilot der Germanwings-Maschine war zu Untersuchungen im Universitätsklinikum Düsseldorf|trans_title=|date=2015-03-27|language=de|access-date=2015-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150401170919/http://www.uniklinik-duesseldorf.de/presse/detailansicht/article/co-pilot-der-germanwings-maschine-war-zu-untersuchungen-im-universitaetsklinikum-duesseldorf|archive-date=2015-04-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。声明显示，卢比茨的情况不适合在当天工作。3月27日，德国检察官查明，卢比茨在空难发生当天曾撕毁病假条，并向航空公司隐瞒患病事实<ref name="qq"/>。

空难发生后的3月26日，德国警方对卢比茨的住所展开搜查<ref>{{cite web|author=Updated 0138 GMT (0938 HKT) March 27, 2015|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/03/26/europe/france-germanwings-plane-crash-main/|title=Germanwings plane crash: Co-pilot acted deliberately|work=CNN|accessdate=2015-03-27|archive-date=2018-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181208202307/https://edition.cnn.com/2015/03/26/europe/france-germanwings-plane-crash-main/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。随后，法国、德国检察官和汉莎航空高管认为卢比茨有摧毁这架飞机的意图<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sky.com/story/1453092/alps-crash-co-pilot-wanted-to-destroy-plane|title=Alps Crash Co-Pilot 'Wanted To Destroy Plane'|work=SKY News|accessdate=2015-03-27|archive-date=2015-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151025081747/http://news.sky.com/story/1453092/alps-crash-co-pilot-wanted-to-destroy-plane|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Clark|first1=Nicola|last2=Bilefsky|first2=Dan|title=Germanwings Co-Pilot Deliberately Crashed Airbus Jet, French Prosecutor Says|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/27/world/europe/germanwings-crash.html|accessdate=2015-03-26|work=The New York Times|date=2015-03-26|archive-date=2018-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180731124012/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/27/world/europe/germanwings-crash.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/mar/26/germanwings-plane-crash-investigation-press-conference-live-updates-4u9525|title=Germanwings Plane Crash Investigation|date=2015-03-26|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2015-03-26|archive-date=2019-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190228171005/https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/mar/26/germanwings-plane-crash-investigation-press-conference-live-updates-4u9525|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/germanwings-flight-4u9525-co-pilot-put-plane-into-descent-prosecutor-says-1.3010045|title=Germanwings Flight 4U9525: Co-pilot put plane into descent, prosecutor says|date=2015-03-26|work=CBC News|accessdate=2015-03-26|archive-date=2015-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326205925/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/germanwings-flight-4u9525-co-pilot-put-plane-into-descent-prosecutor-says-1.3010045|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Levs|first1=Josh|last2=Smith-Spark|first2=Laura|last3=Yan|first3=Holly|title=Germanwings Flight 9525 co-pilot deliberately crashed plane, officials say|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/03/26/europe/france-germanwings-plane-crash-main/index.html|accessdate=2015-03-26|work=SFist|date=2015-03-26|archive-date=2018-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180708223237/https://www.cnn.com/2015/03/26/europe/france-germanwings-plane-crash-main/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月28日，德国警方再次搜查卢比茨的住所，后发现并查扣了若干“治疗心理疾病的药物”<ref name="qq2"/><ref name="auto">{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/03/28/europe/france-germanwings-plane-crash-main/index.html|title=Reports: Antidepressants found at home of co-pilot Andreas Lubitz|work=|date=2015-03-28|accessdate=2015-06-07|archive-date=2018-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180727024330/https://edition.cnn.com/2015/03/28/europe/france-germanwings-plane-crash-main/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Indep29Mar15">{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/andreas-lubitz-repeatedly-urged-germanwings-captain-to-leave-him-alone-in-the-cockpit-before-setting-a320-on-path-to-french-alps-crash-10141732.html|title=Andreas Lubitz 'repeatedly urged Germanwings captain to leave him alone in the cockpit' before setting A320 on path to French Alps crash|work=The Independent|accessdate=2015-03-29|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925185551/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/andreas-lubitz-repeatedly-urged-germanwings-captain-to-leave-him-alone-in-the-cockpit-before-setting-a320-on-path-to-french-alps-crash-10141732.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

