==影響==
加拿大、新西蘭、德國的民航當局迅即實施新規定，要求客機在航行時任何時候必需有兩名獲授權人員留在駕駛艙內<ref name="CBC">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/germanwings-flight-4u9525-canadian-airlines-told-to-have-2-people-in-the-cockpit-1.3010494|title=Germanwings Flight 4U9525: Canadian airlines told to have 2 people in the cockpit|date=2015-03-27|publisher=CBC News|accessdate=2015-03-27|archive-date=2017-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170621055840/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/germanwings-flight-4u9525-canadian-airlines-told-to-have-2-people-in-the-cockpit-1.3010494|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[欧洲航空安全局|欧洲航空安全局]]亦建議類似措施。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/eu-considers-beefing-up-cockpit-rules-after-germanwings-plane-crash-1427455560|title=EU Regulator Recommends Tightening Cockpit Rules After Germanwings Crash|work=The Wall Street Journal|date=2015-03-27|accessdate=2015-03-27|archive-date=2015-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150327155828/http://www.wsj.com/articles/eu-considers-beefing-up-cockpit-rules-after-germanwings-plane-crash-1427455560|dead-url=no}}</ref>多間航空公司也宣佈更改守則落實上述措施。<ref name="CBC" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/mar/26/germanwings-plane-crash-investigation-press-conference-live-updates-4u9525|title=Germanwings crash: airliners change cockpit rules after co-pilot blamed – as it happened|work=The Guardian|date=2015-03-26|accessdate=2015-03-27|archive-date=2019-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190228171005/https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/mar/26/germanwings-plane-crash-investigation-press-conference-live-updates-4u9525|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/mar/27/germanwings-crash-details-emerge-of-the-co-pilot-who-crashed-his-plane-live-updates#block-5514a5ede4b07e0a7c43a7bc|title=Germanwings investigators find torn-up sicknote in co-pilot's home|work=The Guardian|date=2015-03-27|accessdate=2015-03-27|archive-date=2019-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430080212/https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2015/mar/27/germanwings-crash-details-emerge-of-the-co-pilot-who-crashed-his-plane-live-updates#block-5514a5ede4b07e0a7c43a7bc|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="auto1">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/germanwings-flight-4u9525-co-pilot-andreas-lubitz-hid-illness-from-employer-1.3011724|title=Germanwings Flight 4U9525 co-pilot Andreas Lubitz 'hid illness' from employer|publisher=CBC News|date=2015-03-27|accessdate=2015-03-27|archive-date=2017-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170214152437/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/germanwings-flight-4u9525-co-pilot-andreas-lubitz-hid-illness-from-employer-1.3011724|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[美国联邦航空管理局|美国联邦航空管理局]]自2002年已有「必需有兩個人在駕駛艙內」的類似規定。<ref name="auto1"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/27/opinion/reducing-risks-after-the-germanwings-crash.html|title=Reducing Risks After the Germanwings Crash|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2015-03-26|accessdate=2015-03-27|archive-date=2015-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150327050008/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/27/opinion/reducing-risks-after-the-germanwings-crash.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>而[[中国民用航空局|中国民用航空局]]於此事件後，也加強对航班飞行中的驾驶舱机组成员保持数量不少于2人的规定<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20150328/43435506_0.shtml|title=中国民航局：严禁驾驶舱中少于2人|work=[[凤凰网|凤凰网]]|date=2015-03-28|accessdate=2015-03-29|archive-date=2015-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403084003/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20150328/43435506_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==事前預言==
荷蘭機長Jan Cocheret於事發前兩個月在航空專業雜誌《Piloot en Vliegtuig》上撰文，表達強化駕駛艙門的危險。他寫道：「因為有高防護的裝甲駕駛艙門，飛機師現在很容易阻止同事進入駕駛艙。只需要等到同事出去解決生理需要時，讓艙門鎖住打不開。……我常常問自己駕駛艙內坐在我身旁的人是誰，我要如何信任他？說不定他剛經歷人生中無法克服的可怕事件。我希望在小便回來後，永遠不會遇到上鎖駕駛艙門情況。」事發後該機長在臉書上說：「看來這恐怖事情成真了。」<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/jancocheret/posts/855615601148263|title=JanCocheret在脸书上的原文：“Inmiddels is duidelijk dat dit verschrikkelijke verhaal werkelijkheid geworden is...”|accessdate=2017-09-16|author=Jan Cocheret|date=2015-03-26|publisher=|archive-date=2016-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160425170753/https://www.facebook.com/jancocheret/posts/855615601148263|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lefigaro.fr/actualite-france/2015/03/29/01016-20150329ARTFIG00183-crash-a320-un-pilote-neerlandais-avait-prophetise-le-drame.php|title=Crash A320 : un pilote néerlandais avait prophétisé le drame|publisher=Le Figaro|date=2015-03-30|accessdate=2015-03-30|language=fr|archive-date=2015-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150330022729/http://www.lefigaro.fr/actualite-france/2015/03/29/01016-20150329ARTFIG00183-crash-a320-un-pilote-neerlandais-avait-prophetise-le-drame.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.7sur7.be/7s7/fr/1505/Monde/article/detail/2268570/2015/03/28/La-chronique-troublante-d-un-pilote-qui-avait-annonce-le-crash-de-l-Airbus-A320.dhtml|title=La chronique troublante d'un pilote qui avait annoncé le crash de l'Airbus A320|website=7sur7.be|date=2015-03-28|accessdate=2015-03-30|language=fr|archive-date=2015-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150331001309/http://www.7sur7.be/7s7/fr/1505/Monde/article/detail/2268570/2015/03/28/La-chronique-troublante-d-un-pilote-qui-avait-annonce-le-crash-de-l-Airbus-A320.dhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ad.nl/ad/nl/34341/Crash-Airbus-Frankrijk/article/detail/3929068/2015/03/27/Kan-ik-mijn-copiloot-nog-wel-vertrouwen.dhtml|title='Kan ik mijn copiloot nog wel vertrouwen?'|website=ad.nl|date=2015-03-27